001package org.jfree.chart.legend;
002
003
004import org.jfree.chart.api.RectangleAnchor;
005import org.jfree.chart.util.GradientPaintTransformer;
006import org.jfree.chart.internal.Args;
007import java.io.Serializable;
008import org.jfree.chart.api.PublicCloneable;
009
010public class LegendGraphicProduct implements Serializable, PublicCloneable {
011        private RectangleAnchor shapeLocation;
012        private RectangleAnchor shapeAnchor;
013        private GradientPaintTransformer fillPaintTransformer;
014
015        public RectangleAnchor getShapeLocation() {
016                return shapeLocation;
017        }
018
019        public void setShapeLocation2(RectangleAnchor shapeLocation) {
020                this.shapeLocation = shapeLocation;
021        }
022
023        public RectangleAnchor getShapeAnchor() {
024                return shapeAnchor;
025        }
026
027        public void setShapeAnchor2(RectangleAnchor shapeAnchor) {
028                this.shapeAnchor = shapeAnchor;
029        }
030
031        public GradientPaintTransformer getFillPaintTransformer() {
032                return fillPaintTransformer;
033        }
034
035        public void setFillPaintTransformer2(GradientPaintTransformer fillPaintTransformer) {
036                this.fillPaintTransformer = fillPaintTransformer;
037        }
038
039        /**
040        * Sets the transformer used when the fill paint is an instance of {@code  GradientPaint} .
041        * @param transformer   the transformer ( {@code  null}  not permitted).
042        * @see #getFillPaintTransformer()
043        */
044        public void setFillPaintTransformer(GradientPaintTransformer transformer) {
045                Args.nullNotPermitted(transformer, "transformer");
046                this.fillPaintTransformer = transformer;
047        }
048
049        /**
050        * Sets the shape anchor.  This defines a point on the shapes bounding rectangle that will be used to align the shape to a location.
051        * @param anchor   the anchor ( {@code  null}  not permitted).
052        * @see #setShapeAnchor(RectangleAnchor)
053        */
054        public void setShapeAnchor(RectangleAnchor anchor) {
055                Args.nullNotPermitted(anchor, "anchor");
056                this.shapeAnchor = anchor;
057        }
058
059        /**
060        * Sets the shape location.  This defines a point within the drawing area that will be used to align the shape to.
061        * @param location   the location ( {@code  null}  not permitted).
062        * @see #getShapeLocation()
063        */
064        public void setShapeLocation(RectangleAnchor location) {
065                Args.nullNotPermitted(location, "location");
066                this.shapeLocation = location;
067        }
068
069        public Object clone() throws CloneNotSupportedException {
070                return (LegendGraphicProduct) super.clone();
071        }
072}
